title: Change to Eden - Change to Eden
description:
Founded in 1984, Gulfport Mississippi&#039;s Change To Eden has been a force for Progressive Rock for over 20 years. The original line-up of Forrest "By-tor" Miller on drums, Todd Read on bass, Gary Smith on lead guitar, Mark Smith on lead vocals, and David Paul Windham on keyboards, played to sold-out theaters, clubs, and colleges throughout the 1980&#039;s and 90&#039;s.
